Package: doe.workbench
Title: Design of Experiments Workbench
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Stephanie", "Lucas", email = "stephanie.lucas@shell.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")),
    person("Dipesh", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: Interactive Shiny application for Design of Experiments (DoE) and
    regression analysis. Provides tools for experimental design generation,
    model building, ANOVA, effects analysis, residual diagnostics, multiple
    comparisons, robustness checks, and report building. Statistical functions
    are exported for use outside the app.
